OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers or
OL,6,Flonger spells of rain will spread in
OL,7,Fthrough the evening and overnight, the
OL,8,Frain heavy at times. It will be rather
OL,9,Fwindy around the coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FShowers occasionally forming
OL,12,Flonger spells of rain in the morning,
OL,13,Fheavy and thundery at times. Becoming
OL,14,Fdrier and brighter through the
OL,15,Fafternoon as showers fade away. Windy
OL,16,Fat times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
